oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Children with animals and toys
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of three boys and one girl. The girl is holding two dolls, one boy is on a tricycle, and another boy is holding a dog on a leash. The third boy is standing beside a cow that is drinking out of a large pail.
